Table 1. Classification accuracy (%) on (a) Office-Home and (b) VisDA-2017 for unsupervised domain adaptation (using ResNet-50 and

Table 3. Classification accuracy (%) on VisDA-2017 for unsupervised domain adaptation (using ResNet-101 as the backbone).  ? denotes
